data.description: Perched on a ridge above the Cle Elum Valley is this incredible rambler, w/180 degree, panoramic views! The single level home is the perfect size for year 'round OR seasonal living. Expansive southern facing great room for all day light! Massive living space features a 2 story fireplace & exposed wood beams. The dining area has a view to wow any dinner guests! Well appointed kitchen w/island eating bar & custom pantry. The Primary Suite has a spa-like bath; corner jetted tub, separate tiled shower, walk-in closet, & view deck. There are also 2 additional guest rooms & a full guest bath. Powder Room + 3 car attached garage.  Oversized crawlspace for extra storage or wine cellar. Tons of outdoor entertaining space. Treed, private, must see.
